{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NTA5Ng_0006","text":"我那天經過碰着你 你笑得比這世上美","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":16},"semantics":{"themes":["邂逅","吸引","美好"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["經過","碰著","你","笑","美"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,3,3,4,4,2,5,5,4,3,9,5,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","naa5","tin1","ging1","gwo3","pung3","zoek6","nei5","nei5","siu3","dak1","bei2","ze5","sai3","mei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"那天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"經過","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"碰着","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"笑","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"得","pos":"PART"},{"text":"比","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"世上","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"美","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「你笑得比這世上美」是極高的讚美，直接點出對方的美麗和吸引力。"},"source":{"title":"接近","artists":["陳慧嫺"],"lyricists":["張學友","潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5096","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NTA5Ng_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NTA5Ng_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NTA5Ng_0007","text":"叫我不得不追求你","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["追求","吸引力","愛慕"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["追求","你"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,5,3,3,3,3,0,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["giu3","ngo5","bat1","dak1","bat1","zeoi1","kau4","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"叫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"不得不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"追求","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"「不得不」表達一種強烈的、無法抗拒的吸引力，促使採取行動。"},"source":{"title":"接近","artists":["陳慧嫺"],"lyricists":["張學友","潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5096","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NTA5Ng_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NTA5Ng_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NTA5Ng_0008","text":"世界中一切亦無味 不一起","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["失落","孤獨","愛情"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["世界","無味","不一起"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,4,3,3,4,2,0,2,3,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["sai3","gaai3","zung1","jat1","cai3","jik6","mou4","mei6","bat1","jat1","hei2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"世界","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"中","pos":"PART"},{"text":"一切","pos":"DET"},{"text":"亦","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"無味","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"一起","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「一切亦無味，不一起」強烈對比了有對方與無對方的感受，表達孤單和失落。"},"source":{"title":"接近","artists":["陳慧嫺"],"lyricists":["張學友","潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5096","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NTA5Ng_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NTA5Ng_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
